video_title: Want to Be Successful? Do This!
transcript:
hey you want a simple strategy to be
more successful well Harvard did a study
in the 1970s with their graduating class
and found out that out of the entire
class only three percent of them wrote
down their goals ten years later they
followed up with all of those students
and found out that those three percent
that wrote down their goals were 10
times more financially successful than
the other 97 percent combined why is
that because when you write down your
goals it makes them real it makes them
physically exist in this world and when
it's on paper it can be planned so if
you really want to be successful here's
the key write down your goals
